am(f32),"},{"DocComment":"     Pound(f32),"},{"DocComment":" }"},{"DocComment":""},{"DocComment":" struct Balance {"},{"DocComment":"     pub left: Weight,"},{"DocComment":"     pub right: Weight,"},{"DocComment":" }"},{"DocComment":""},{"DocComment":" impl Index<Side> for Balance {"},{"DocComment":"     type Output = Weight;"},{"DocComment":""},{"DocComment":"     fn index(&self, index: Side) -> &Self::Output {"},{"DocComment":"         println!(\"Accessing {index:?}-side of balance immutably\");"},{"DocComment":"         match index {"},{"DocComment":"             Side::Left => &self.left,"},{"DocComment":"             Side::Right => &self.right,"},{"DocComment":"         }"},{"DocComment":"     }"},{"DocComment":" }"},{"DocComment":""},{"DocComment":" impl IndexMut<Side> for Balance {"},{"DocComment":"     fn index_mut(&mut self, index: Side) -> &mut Self::Output {"},{"DocComment":"         println!(\"Accessing {index:?}-side of balance mutably\");"},{"DocComment":"         match index {"},{"DocComment":"             Side::Left => &mut self.left,"},{"DocComment":"             Side::Right => &mut self.right,"},{"DocComment":"         }"},{"DocComment":"     }"},{"DocComment":" }"},{"DocComment":""},{"DocComment":" let mut balance = Balance {"},{"DocComment":"     right: Weight::Kilogram(2.5),"},{"DocComment":"     left: Weight::Pound(1.5),"},{"DocComment":" };"},{"DocComment":""},{"DocComment":" // In this case, `balance[Side::Right]` is sugar for"},{"DocComment":" // `*balance.index(Side::Right)`, since we are only *reading*"},{"DocComment":" // `balance[Side::Right]`, not writing it."},{"DocComment":" assert_eq!(balance[Side::Right], Weight::Kilogram(2.5));"},{"DocComment":""},{"DocComment":" // However, in this case `balance[Side::Left]` is sugar for"},{"DocComment":" // `*balance.index_mut(Side::Left)`, since we are writing"},{"DocComment":" // `balance[Side::Left]`."},{"DocComment":" balance[Side::Left] = Weight::Kilogram(3.0);"},{"DocComment":" ```"}],"inlin